      <title>Front Matter add multiple tag</title>
      <link href="/2020/06/23/Front-Matter-add-multiple-tag/"/>
      <url>/2020/06/23/Front-Matter-add-multiple-tag/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><strong>如何为当前文章设置多个tag？</strong></p><p>在tag标签后按照下面样子写就可以了</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">tags:</span> <span class="string">[标签1,</span> <span class="string">标签2,</span> <span class="string">标签3]</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>实际使用的效果如下：</p><p><img src="multiple_tags.jpg" alt=""></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> tags </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
